00:15:08,540 --> 00:15:09,900
We'll squeeze into one.

283
00:15:09,900 --> 00:15:11,380
What do you mean?

284
00:15:11,660 --> 00:15:12,500
A room.

285
00:15:12,500 --> 00:15:13,420
A small one will do.

286
00:15:13,580 --> 00:15:14,420
Yes, yes.

287
00:15:15,540 --> 00:15:16,380
Mom.

288
00:15:16,580 --> 00:15:17,420
Well.

289
00:15:19,660 --> 00:15:21,780
Can we use this to pay for the room?

290
00:15:25,620 --> 00:15:27,140
It's pure 24-karat gold.

291
00:15:27,540 --> 00:15:29,300
Yes, no problem.

292
00:15:30,020 --> 00:15:30,860
That's great.

293
00:15:31,820 --> 00:15:33,900
(Earth Room 1)

294
00:15:40,860 --> 00:15:42,300
The challenge we faced today

295
00:15:42,900 --> 00:15:44,300
is the most severe one

296
00:15:44,740 --> 00:15:46,460
our family has ever encountered.

297
00:15:46,860 --> 00:15:48,980
So, today's family meeting

298
00:15:49,220 --> 00:15:50,420
is to discuss

299
00:15:50,900 --> 00:15:52,140
what we should do next.

300
00:16:04,220 --> 00:16:05,420
Shen Jianshe,

301
00:16:05,780 --> 00:16:07,580
you start with some constructive advice.

302
00:16:08,100 --> 00:16:09,780
I'll just say a few things briefly.

303
00:16:11,140 --> 00:16:13,140
The challenge we faced today

304
00:16:13,420 --> 00:16:14,940
is the most severe one

305
00:16:14,940 --> 00:16:16,300
our family has ever encountered.

306
00:16:16,300 --> 00:16:18,140
We need to look at this issue

307
00:16:18,260 --> 00:16:19,980
comprehensively and objectively.

308
00:16:20,740 --> 00:16:21,620
As for what

309
00:16:21,620 --> 00:16:23,260
we should do next,

310
00:16:23,660 --> 00:16:26,500
I think we should go back first.

311
00:16:26,940 --> 00:16:27,780
That's it?

312
00:16:27,900 --> 00:16:28,820
That's it.

313
00:16:28,820 --> 00:16:30,020
All nonsense.

314
00:16:31,540 --> 00:16:33,300
I knew I couldn't count on you.

315
00:16:34,390 --> 00:16:35,780
Hey, Shen Gongcai.

316
00:16:35,780 --> 00:16:36,780
Give your opinion.

317
00:16:39,860 --> 00:16:41,300
How to go back

318
00:16:41,660 --> 00:16:42,820
is especially important.

319
00:16:43,700 --> 00:16:45,460
We need to analyze it carefully,

320
00:16:45,740 --> 00:16:47,500
but I really can't come up
with anything.

321
00:16:47,820 --> 00:16:49,820
Fortunately, Jicai came with us.

322
00:16:50,220 --> 00:16:51,080
She's good at history.

323
00:16:51,120 --> 00:16:52,740
She knows
how to exchange gold for money.

324
00:16:52,740 --> 00:16:55,220
Otherwise, we might all be in jail now.

325
00:16:55,300 --> 00:16:56,580
All nonsense.

326
00:16:57,140 --> 00:16:58,660
I knew I couldn't count on you.

327
00:16:59,940 --> 00:17:01,740
Dear, let me discipline him for you.

328
00:17:01,740 --> 00:17:03,820
If you don't speak,
no one will think you're mute.

329
00:17:06,700 --> 00:17:07,540
Jicai,

330
00:17:07,980 --> 00:17:08,940
you tell us.

331
00:17:09,540 --> 00:17:11,260
Based on the map we saw

332
00:17:11,260 --> 00:17:12,460
at Yunshui Manor,

333
00:17:12,940 --> 00:17:14,580
the manor is in that direction.

334
00:17:14,900 --> 00:17:16,900
Since we came through Yunshui Manor,

335
00:17:17,110 --> 00:17:18,920
we need to go there
to figure something out.

336
00:17:19,820 --> 00:17:21,060
Yunshui Manor...

337
00:17:23,660 --> 00:17:25,290
(Yunshui Manor)

338
00:17:25,290 --> 00:17:26,620
Round 1.

339
00:17:26,620 --> 00:17:28,140
Can this get us in?

340
00:17:28,620 --> 00:17:30,260
We have to try.

341
00:17:31,300 --> 00:17:32,140
Stop!

342
00:17:33,940 --> 00:17:35,980
This is the private residence
of the Vice Prefect.

343
00:17:36,060 --> 00:17:36,900
You can't enter.

344
00:17:41,500 --> 00:17:42,340
Sir,

345
00:17:42,660 --> 00:17:43,740
please let us in.

346
00:17:44,020 --> 00:17:45,780
This is pure 24-karat gold.

347
00:17:45,860 --> 00:17:46,700
Go!

348
00:17:48,060 --> 00:17:49,100
Why would you risk bribery

349
00:17:49,100 --> 00:17:51,180
just to break into the mansion

350
00:17:51,180 --> 00:17:52,020
of the Vice Prefect?

351
00:17:52,140 --> 00:17:53,300
Don't get excited.

352
00:17:53,620 --> 00:17:54,980
My mother has hysteria.

353
00:17:55,060 --> 00:17:56,380
I'm taking her home right away.

354
00:17:57,680 --> 00:17:58,940
You're about to have an episode.

355
00:17:58,940 --> 00:18:00,580
Let's go home.

356
00:18:00,700 --> 00:18:04,660
(Day 3)

357
00:18:06,820 --> 00:18:08,380
- Here.
- Thank you.

358
00:18:08,380 --> 00:18:09,220
Take it.

359
00:18:11,120 --> 00:18:12,460
Round 2.

360
00:18:16,820 --> 00:18:17,740
Did you see anything?

361
00:18:17,740 --> 00:18:18,660
What are you doing?

362
00:18:19,940 --> 00:18:20,940
It's none of my business.

363
00:18:21,180 --> 00:18:22,460
- Stop!
- None of my business.

364
00:18:22,460 --> 00:18:23,300
Stop!

365
00:18:24,100 --> 00:18:25,220
Gongcai!

366
00:18:28,020 --> 00:18:30,060
(Day 5)

367
00:18:30,060 --> 00:18:30,900
Here.

368
00:18:41,260 --> 00:18:42,570
Round 3.

369
00:18:49,060 --> 00:18:50,140
It seems no one's around.

370
00:18:50,460 --> 00:18:51,660
If no one's here, move aside.

371
00:18:51,660 --> 00:18:52,500
Let me do it.

372
00:19:00,540 --> 00:19:01,620
Hurry, hurry.

373
00:19:02,820 --> 00:19:04,220
(Day...)

374
00:19:04,220 --> 00:19:05,700
We don't have much money left.

375
00:19:06,420 --> 00:19:07,380
Let's save

376
00:19:07,540 --> 00:19:08,900
half of this pancake for tomorrow.

377
00:19:09,460 --> 00:19:11,460
Eating pancakes every day.

378
00:19:11,460 --> 00:19:12,900
I'm about to go crazy.

379
00:19:12,900 --> 00:19:14,820
I really can't eat another bite.

380
00:19:14,880 --> 00:19:15,740
You won't eat it?

381
00:19:15,860 --> 00:19:17,060
Then let me have it.

382
00:19:17,300 --> 00:19:18,780
Having pancakes is not bad at all.

383
00:19:18,900 --> 00:19:19,860
Besides,

384
00:19:19,940 --> 00:19:21,020
right now, our whole family

385
00:19:21,100 --> 00:19:22,580
is relying on your mom's

386
00:19:22,580 --> 00:19:23,940
gold jewelry.

387
00:19:24,380 --> 00:19:25,220
We have to save.

388
00:19:26,020 --> 00:19:27,060
Isn't that right, Fengxia?

389
00:19:27,740 --> 00:19:28,740
That makes sense.

390
00:19:32,120 --> 00:19:34,140
Everyone, I've found out
from the shopkeeper

391
00:19:34,300 --> 00:19:35,320
that our ancestor Lin Yan

392
00:19:35,360 --> 00:19:36,300
is about to take office

393
00:19:36,300 --> 00:19:37,580
and will soon enter the Capital.

394
00:19:37,580 --> 00:19:38,420
Really?

395
00:19:39,180 --> 00:19:40,220
That's great!

396
00:19:40,340 --> 00:19:41,660
He should be responsible for us.

397
00:19:41,660 --> 00:19:43,860
He can't just bring us into this world
and ignore us.

398
00:19:43,860 --> 00:19:44,700
Everyone,

399
00:19:44,940 --> 00:19:46,180
hope is coming.

400
00:19:47,620 --> 00:19:48,490
Let's have a meeting.

401
00:19:48,540 --> 00:19:49,700
A meeting.

402
00:19:50,060 --> 00:19:51,500
Jicai.

403
00:19:51,620 --> 00:19:53,340
Come and sit here.

404
00:19:53,340 --> 00:19:55,010
- Jicai.
- I'm fine where.

405
00:19:55,260 --> 00:19:57,060
- We need to talk.
- Dad.

406
00:19:57,060 --> 00:19:58,060
- What for?
- The usual.

407
00:19:58,380 --> 00:19:59,250
It's nothing.

408
00:19:59,270 --> 00:20:00,420
Auntie, come here.

409
00:20:04,740 --> 00:20:06,140
- Listen to me.
- Okay.

410
00:20:06,220 --> 00:20:07,860
Before, the master wasn't home,

411
00:20:07,880 --> 00:20:08,740
so the guards

412
00:20:08,740 --> 00:20:09,980
didn't dare let us in.

413
00:20:10,300 --> 00:20:11,660
If Lin Yan arrives,

414
00:20:12,140 --> 00:20:13,460
and we get close to him,

415
00:20:13,620 --> 00:20:15,380
then we might have a chance to go home.

416
00:20:16,060 --> 00:20:17,340
That's what I mean.

417
00:20:20,020 --> 00:20:21,740
Now, there's a more serious problem.

418
00:20:22,380 --> 00:20:23,220
What problem?

419
00:20:25,340 --> 00:20:26,340
Gold

420
00:20:26,580 --> 00:20:27,940
will eventually run out.

421
00:20:28,060 --> 00:20:29,620
We'll soon have no money left.

422
00:20:30,260 --> 00:20:32,820
We need to find a way
to make some money.

423
00:20:33,100 --> 00:20:33,940
Shen Jianshe,

424
00:20:35,460 --> 00:20:36,660
I hope you can give

425
00:20:36,820 --> 00:20:38,780
some constructive ideas
on how to make money.

426
00:20:39,140 --> 00:20:39,980
Me?

427
00:20:40,700 --> 00:20:41,540
Well.

428
00:20:42,060 --> 00:20:43,500
Why is it always me?

429
00:20:43,940 --> 00:20:45,180
Well, I think

430
00:20:45,540 --> 00:20:46,540
making money

431
00:20:46,540 --> 00:20:47,860
is out of the question.

432
00:20:48,540 --> 00:20:49,780
We just have to save money.

433
00:20:50,020 --> 00:20:52,020
To save money, you have to eat less.

434
00:20:52,140 --> 00:20:53,980
If you eat less, you move less.

435
00:20:54,060 --> 00:20:55,000
Best not to move at all.

436
00:20:55,060 --> 00:20:56,580
If you don't move, you won't be hungry.

437
00:20:56,580 --> 00:20:58,340
If you're not hungry,
you won't spend money.

438
00:20:58,420 --> 00:20:59,380
Listen

439
00:20:59,380 --> 00:21:00,620
to what you're saying.

440
00:21:00,790 --> 00:21:01,660
Do you realize now

441
00:21:01,660 --> 00:21:02,900
how you managed

442
00:21:02,900 --> 00:21:04,420
to ruin our diner?

443
00:21:04,420 --> 00:21:05,540
Is that thing on your neck

444
00:21:05,540 --> 00:21:06,740
just for show?

445
00:21:06,820 --> 00:21:08,420
What kind of silly idea is that?

446
00:21:08,700 --> 00:21:09,860
Mom, no, no.

447
00:21:09,940 --> 00:21:11,260
Don't get worked up.

448
00:21:11,540 --> 00:21:13,100
What Dad is trying to say

449
00:21:13,100 --> 00:21:14,140
is about cutting expenses

450
00:21:14,340 --> 00:21:15,580
and increasing income.

451
00:21:15,680 --> 00:21:16,580
Well.

452
00:21:16,620 --> 00:21:18,420
Dad is just not very articulate.

453
00:21:18,740 --> 00:21:20,340
Dad, that's not right.

454
00:21:20,340 --> 00:21:21,940
Get up.

455
00:21:21,940 --> 00:21:23,760
What are you saying?
Mom has explained it,

456
00:21:23,760 --> 00:21:25,020
and you still don't understand?

457
00:21:25,100 --> 00:21:26,140
At such a critical moment,

458
00:21:26,180 --> 00:21:27,260
how can you say that?

459
00:21:27,260 --> 00:21:28,140
As usual.

460
00:21:28,140 --> 00:21:29,340
I just spoke up for you again.

461
00:21:29,340 --> 00:21:30,460
Give me another 20.

462
00:21:30,460 --> 00:21:31,700
I don't have any money.

463
00:21:31,820 --> 00:21:32,820
Will you give it to me?

464
00:21:32,820 --> 00:21:34,100
I really don't have any.

465
00:21:34,620 --> 00:21:35,860
Mom, what Dad actually meant...

466
00:21:35,860 --> 00:21:36,700
Gongcai.

467
00:21:37,820 --> 00:21:39,140
You just made

468
00:21:39,380 --> 00:21:40,500
a point.

469
00:21:44,660 --> 00:21:47,300
What Dad actually meant

470
00:21:47,500 --> 00:21:49,100
was that he should've brought

471
00:21:49,100 --> 00:21:51,540
some gold or silver

472
00:21:51,940 --> 00:21:53,080
to ease our worries, right?

473
00:21:53,080 --> 00:21:54,220
- Yes.
- He meant that.

474
00:21:54,220 --> 00:21:55,460
Could he have thought of that?

475
00:21:55,580 --> 00:21:56,860
- I was just thinking.
- Gold?

476
00:21:57,340 --> 00:21:58,460
I have gold, too.

477
00:22:00,580 --> 00:22:02,460
Great-grandpa gave it to me.

478
00:22:05,980 --> 00:22:07,260
Before our ancestor takes office,

479
00:22:07,260 --> 00:22:09,140
we need to find a way to survive.

480
00:22:09,140 --> 00:22:10,020
How about

481
00:22:10,140 --> 00:22:11,380
going back to the old business?

482
00:22:11,380 --> 00:22:12,220
Why don't we

483
00:22:12,460 --> 00:22:13,940
set up a small stall

484
00:22:14,260 --> 00:22:15,220
and sell some snacks?

485
00:22:15,620 --> 00:22:16,500
I can do that.

486
00:22:16,780 --> 00:22:18,260
Can we make Jianbing Guozi?

487
00:22:18,420 --> 00:22:20,140
I love Jianbing Guozi the most.

488
00:22:23,180 --> 00:22:24,940
That's a good idea.

489
00:22:26,620 --> 00:22:27,500
Let's split up.

490
00:22:27,860 --> 00:22:29,960
Yangyang and I will try
to get close to our ancestor

491
00:22:30,020 --> 00:22:31,360
and find a way into Yunshui Manor.

492
00:22:31,700 --> 00:22:33,340
You guys set up the stall
and make money.

493
00:22:34,020 --> 00:22:34,860
I've got an idea

494
00:22:35,140 --> 00:22:36,760
that's sure
to make Jianbing Guozi a hit.

495
00:22:43,220 --> 00:22:45,660
(Xuanzheng Hall)

496
00:22:47,820 --> 00:22:50,780
I've heard that the newly appointed
Vice Prefect Lin Yan

497
00:22:51,220 --> 00:22:52,660
is not from a prestigious family,

498
00:22:52,880 --> 00:22:54,580
nor did he study
under any famous mentors.

499
00:22:54,660 --> 00:22:55,700
He's made his way up

500
00:22:55,900 --> 00:22:57,420
entirely on his own merits

501
00:22:57,540 --> 00:22:58,660
without any patronage.

502
00:22:58,940 --> 00:23:01,220
His Majesty has promoted him
by exception

503
00:23:01,420 --> 00:23:04,060
and even granted him
a jade belt and a gold fish token,

504
00:23:04,060 --> 00:23:05,500
making him like a Rank III official.

505
00:23:06,300 --> 00:23:07,200
I've also heard

506
00:23:07,220 --> 00:23:09,900
that His Majesty
even decided his salary,

507
00:23:10,260 --> 00:23:11,860
equivalent to a Rank II official.

508
00:23:11,860 --> 00:23:15,820
(Lin Yan, Vice Prefect
of Capital Prefecture)

509
00:23:15,820 --> 00:23:19,380
Mr. Lin is extremely talented
and handsome.

510
00:23:19,580 --> 00:23:21,980
(Mr. Meng, Left Supervisor)
Your granddaughter

511
00:23:21,980 --> 00:23:23,500
is of marriageable age.

512
00:23:23,980 --> 00:23:27,420
Why don't you ask him?

513
00:23:27,780 --> 00:23:28,960
There will be so many suitors

514
00:23:29,060 --> 00:23:31,500
that his doorstep will be worn down.

515
00:23:31,660 --> 00:23:32,700
I'm afraid

516
00:23:32,980 --> 00:23:35,340
I can't match up.

517
00:23:35,860 --> 00:23:37,540
You must be joking.

518
00:23:38,700 --> 00:23:41,220
- Vice Prefect Lin.
- Vice Prefect Lin.

519
00:23:44,570 --> 00:23:46,300
You flatter me.

520
00:23:46,560 --> 00:23:47,540
We're outside the hall.

521
00:23:47,540 --> 00:23:48,380
I'm the junior here.

522
00:23:48,820 --> 00:23:50,500
I should greet you all first.

523
00:23:51,300 --> 00:23:52,340
It's fine.

524
00:24:00,300 --> 00:24:02,900
His Majesty is not feeling well today,

525
00:24:03,660 --> 00:24:05,900
so please go back.

526
00:24:06,580 --> 00:24:08,900
His Majesty won't listen
to reports today.

527
00:24:09,620 --> 00:24:11,420
Vice Prefect Lin, wait a moment.

528
00:24:11,780 --> 00:24:14,580
His Majesty has asked you to see him.

529
00:24:26,220 --> 00:24:29,940
(Emperor Yuanfeng)

530
00:24:36,660 --> 00:24:37,500
Your Majesty.

531
00:24:48,940 --> 00:24:50,060
Since you're unwell,

532
00:24:50,300 --> 00:24:51,180
you should rest.

533
00:24:51,660 --> 00:24:53,420
Why call me to play Chupu?

534
00:24:54,180 --> 00:24:55,820
Eunuch Qin, please take it away.

535
00:24:56,340 --> 00:24:57,180
Don't.

536
00:24:58,300 --> 00:24:59,820
Alright, alright.

537
00:25:00,060 --> 00:25:01,860
I won't cheat.

538
00:25:02,330 --> 00:25:04,300
Just finish this game.

539
00:25:04,900 --> 00:25:06,140
I'm already in the Capital.

540
00:25:06,580 --> 00:25:08,020
I'm ready to play anytime.

541
00:25:08,620 --> 00:25:09,460
But right now,

542
00:25:09,700 --> 00:25:11,720
there's something more important
I need to report.

543
00:25:13,380 --> 00:25:15,380
You're using official business
to block me.

544
00:25:17,900 --> 00:25:18,740
Go ahead.

545
00:25:19,620 --> 00:25:21,740
You asked me to handle
the embezzlement case

546
00:25:21,740 --> 00:25:23,500
of disaster relief funds
in Huaiyuan County.

547
00:25:23,740 --> 00:25:25,980
The ringleader is the local magistrate.

548
00:25:26,700 --> 00:25:28,300
He wanted to redeem his crime with gold,

549
00:25:28,340 --> 00:25:29,340
but I rejected it.

550
00:25:29,620 --> 00:25:31,380
He was beheaded two days ago.

551
00:25:31,700 --> 00:25:33,660
You've done a good job.

552
00:25:34,620 --> 00:25:36,020
But the surname of this magistrate

553
00:25:36,420 --> 00:25:37,500
is Dou,

554
00:25:39,020 --> 00:25:40,940
and he is a relative
of Noble Consort Dou.

555
00:25:42,660 --> 00:25:43,660
Lin Yan,

556
00:25:44,340 --> 00:25:45,300
how dare you!

557
00:25:54,140 --> 00:25:55,020
Please let me explain.

558
00:25:55,500 --> 00:25:57,800
The amount of pepper stored
in Magistrate Dou's residence

559
00:25:57,860 --> 00:25:58,460
is enormous,

560
00:25:58,780 --> 00:26:01,220
enough to supply
the East and West Areas for four years.

561
00:26:01,300 --> 00:26:02,380
The price of pepper per jin

562
00:26:02,380 --> 00:26:03,640
is far more valuable than gold.

563
00:26:03,900 --> 00:26:06,020
At that time,
the displaced people suffered greatly.

564
00:26:06,060 --> 00:26:07,300
The commoners couldn't get food,

565
00:26:07,420 --> 00:26:08,860
and even exchanged children for food.

566
00:26:09,380 --> 00:26:11,500
If such a huge embezzler
could be spared from death,

