00:35:52,650 --> 00:35:54,500
just joking with you.

853
00:35:54,940 --> 00:35:55,860
These pancakes

854
00:35:56,580 --> 00:35:57,940
are all one qian each.

855
00:35:57,940 --> 00:35:58,780
- One?
- Okay.

856
00:35:58,780 --> 00:36:00,220
- One qian?
- That's right.

857
00:36:00,380 --> 00:36:01,220
That's right.

858
00:36:01,380 --> 00:36:02,220
Go, go, go.

859
00:36:02,780 --> 00:36:03,620
Ancestor.

860
00:36:03,650 --> 00:36:04,500
Am I dreaming?

861
00:36:04,500 --> 00:36:05,900
We saw our ancestor here.

862
00:36:05,900 --> 00:36:06,990
I'll take one, please.

863
00:36:07,000 --> 00:36:08,460
My goodness.

864
00:36:08,640 --> 00:36:09,820
Ancestor.

865
00:36:10,500 --> 00:36:11,920
No pushing.

866
00:36:11,920 --> 00:36:13,540
No need to rush; everyone will get some.

867
00:36:13,540 --> 00:36:14,380
My shoe fell off.

868
00:36:24,940 --> 00:36:27,060
Don't worry; everyone will get some.

869
00:36:29,340 --> 00:36:31,020
Auntie.

870
00:36:53,220 --> 00:36:54,060
Please make way.

871
00:36:54,180 --> 00:36:55,220
Excuse me.

872
00:36:56,700 --> 00:36:57,820
I haven't bought yet.

873
00:36:57,970 --> 00:36:59,090
- Auntie.
- Don't leave.

874
00:36:59,090 --> 00:37:00,340
I still want to buy.

875
00:37:00,500 --> 00:37:03,110
- Vice Prefect, wait.
- Don't leave.

876
00:37:05,890 --> 00:37:06,940
Be careful!

877
00:37:37,820 --> 00:37:39,860
(Shaoguang's Food Notes)

878
00:37:39,860 --> 00:37:46,420
(The pancake has been upgraded
to five colors.)

879
00:37:46,430 --> 00:37:53,430
(But why hasn't the ancestor come?)

880
00:38:30,610 --> 00:38:33,940
♪Wear a sunset glow upon the brow♪

881
00:38:33,940 --> 00:38:37,200
♪Breeze sways,
wind chimes hang below the cloud♪

882
00:38:37,520 --> 00:38:40,540
♪Hear one chime ring,
tugging at the heart♪

883
00:38:40,540 --> 00:38:43,640
♪True feelings perhaps
can only be sensed♪

884
00:38:44,220 --> 00:38:47,650
♪Misty is you, clear is you♪

885
00:38:47,650 --> 00:38:51,070
♪Seeking stars in fog,
seeing your shadow under the moon♪

886
00:38:51,070 --> 00:38:54,460
♪Words held back, feelings unrestrained♪

887
00:38:54,460 --> 00:38:59,610
♪Could the road ahead,
let us gaze but not doubt♪

888
00:39:01,570 --> 00:39:04,710
♪Mistook all eyes see as cold ice♪

889
00:39:04,710 --> 00:39:08,110
♪Yet let dusk dye
the ears and temples red♪

890
00:39:08,350 --> 00:39:11,410
♪Even holding breath
couldn't help but stop♪

891
00:39:11,410 --> 00:39:14,460
♪Exposing my warmed heart held tight♪

892
00:39:15,050 --> 00:39:18,510
♪Bustling is you, desolate is you♪

893
00:39:18,510 --> 00:39:21,890
♪Reservedly drawing you into this life♪

894
00:39:21,890 --> 00:39:25,320
♪Hesitating, undecided,
the heart hard to deceive♪

895
00:39:25,320 --> 00:39:31,140
♪Worldly rules and taboos,
how could they make me give up♪

896
00:39:31,380 --> 00:39:35,750
♪When rushing to you,
leaving my deep thoughts in disarray♪

897
00:39:35,750 --> 00:39:38,020
♪I still foolishly see it
as a good time♪

898
00:39:38,020 --> 00:39:42,340
♪Heart stirs,
wind swirls the lightest ripples♪

899
00:39:42,340 --> 00:39:45,110
♪A thousand tangled thoughts concealed♪

900
00:39:45,110 --> 00:39:49,390
♪Saved a whole lifetime,
hastening to you, urgent over miles♪

901
00:39:49,390 --> 00:39:52,830
♪To make the wandering heart
return home henceforth♪

902
00:39:52,830 --> 00:39:56,270
♪To draw near what seems beyond reach♪

903
00:39:56,270 --> 00:40:01,120
♪Through life and death changes,
only we never cease, never yield♪

904
00:40:01,120 --> 00:40:05,840
♪Perhaps affection barely passes muster♪

905
00:40:05,840 --> 00:40:08,010
♪But love forever♪

906
00:40:08,020 --> 00:40:13,780
♪Will make up for our mutual care,
mutual bond♪

907
00:40:14,060 --> 00:40:18,600
♪Saved a whole lifetime,
hastening to you, urgent over miles♪

908
00:40:18,600 --> 00:40:21,960
♪To make the wandering heart
return home from now♪

909
00:40:21,960 --> 00:40:25,430
♪To dare approach
what seems beyond reach♪

910
00:40:25,430 --> 00:40:27,170
♪Through life and death changes♪

911
00:40:27,170 --> 00:40:33,530
♪Only you, never cease, never yield♪

